Peanut Butter cookies

1 large egg
1 c creamy peanut butter
1 c sugar
flaky sea salt (optional)

Preheat oven to 350F. Beat egg with a whisk in a medium bowl. Add peanut butter and sugar and whisk until fully incorporated and smooth. If using salt, sprinkle cookies after making crosshatch with fork. Bake cookies, rotating trays halfway through, until golden brown, 10â€“12 min.

Notes: gluten-free
